We can use script called ReconSpider.py to crawl the site and collect the data like files, URL, Emails 

Step 1) Install scapry 
        pip3 install scrapy
Step 2) Install ReconSpider
        wget -O ReconSpider.zip https://academy.hackthebox.com/storage/modules/144/ReconSpider.v1.2.zip
        unzip ReconSpider.zip 

Step 3) Run the program 
        python3 ReconSpider.py http://inlanefreight.com

Step 4) Output is saved as results.json
        
